liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Another absolutely nothing dismissal, just hanging the bat out at a wide one and chopping on. Usman Khawaja's brilliant Test ends in meek fashion on 65. Stokes pulled up seriously lame after that one. I think he might hook himself after that now.
